addPagesFilter

public void addPagesFilter()
Creates and adds a miFilter to the toolbar. Does not bind it to the grid store.

enableContextCommonToolItems

public final void enableContextCommonToolItems(boolean enabled,
                                               boolean inherited,
                                               boolean designed)
Enables or disables the toolbar common items which need a model context (i.e. a selected page), according to passed param value.
The involved items are: "Edit Page", "Delete Page", "Design" and "Preview"

Parameters:
enabled - if true enables, otherwise disables.
inherited - if true disables delete button.
designed - if true design button can be enabled
